    "text": "Thanks Stew, that's about it. Note that one subgraph produces 42 the integer and the other \"Alice\" the string, the result is then of type &lt;int | string&gt;, a variant type of either type. One could also write this as an expression: `global-&gt;frame = 15 ? \"Alice\" : 42` and wrap/unwrap from one to the other.",
